descript.abstract: The dataset represents the boundaries of the FAO Fishing Areas. The source for the boundaries is the description that can be found on the FAO website (http://www.oceansatlas.org/servlet/CDSServlet?status=ND0zMTA2JmN0bl9pbmZvX3ZpZXdfc2l6ZT1jdG5faW5mb192aWV3X2Z1bGwmNj1lbiYzMz0qJjM3PWtvcw~~).

procstep.procdesc: Making of a waterbackground: based on the World Countries 2004 dataset was a waterbackground made. This is one polygon that contains all the ocean and sea features of the world.
Dividing of the waterbackground in individual fishing areas based on the description on the FAO website.
